latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Miss Supranational Asia 2022 ♾
Words seem short to truly express how loved I feel today. To every single person that supported me, my heart is yours. You will never know how much it means to me so here’s the biggest thank you. @misssupranational my most cherished experience ever, you’ve given me more than what lies in a competition, a gift for a lifetime! 
@missdivaorg you have been the best team ever, backed me up and how, I am here only because of you my A-team! @vineetjain12 grateful to you eternally for the opportunities, encouragement and belief to no ends. Immense respect & honour to you! @naughtynatty_g can never thank you enough for being the backbone, driving force and the change maker of my journey. I love you forever boss woman. Upwards & onwards. 
Put in every ounce of my blood, sweat & tears but I believe everything happens for a reason kyuki picture abhi baaki hai. Hope I’ve done you proud India. 
- Ri <3

Only the moon & sky full of stars know! 🕊 
Can’t even begin to express how thankful I am right now! *teary eyes* This is just not my victory but ours! Here’s to every individual that supported, Inspired, encouraged me to no ends. Your love, wishes & blessings made me win! I love you all beyond words! To the pageant community, y’all have my heart! 
Here’s to new beginnings! @missdivaorg  I write to you with a heart filled with immense gratitude for believing in me! @vineetjain12 Sir & @naughtynatty_g ma’am, To making you proud every step of the way! Life truly is magical, here’s to being unstoppable, powerful & limitless! @misssupranational Can’t wait to embark on this incredible journey representing 1.3 billion people, this time it’s ours! 
I love you all xx 🤞❤️🇮🇳✨👼
- God’s child!
Just … 🌅🩷🫶☀️🥞🌻
